	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Spellbreakers dedicate their lives to hunting mages and magical creatures. Though all rangers are skilled at tracking and regularly fight creatures with magical power, spellbreakers focus on hampering or outright disabling the magical abilities of their foes. Some are zealots who hate or fear magic, but most spellbreakers only hunt mages or magical creatures who get out of control or threaten innocents.</em></p><table><caption><p>The Spellbreaker</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p>Level</p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p>Features</p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.DTO0IEWtZxQvqJrP]{Magic Shackles}, @UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.rZ0yficcpohjcvKx]{Mark of Breaking}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>6</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.ephwTM1iSjPPaJkn]{Cleanse Magic}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>11</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.Xe51IME6ys6WoC9f]{Rend Magic}</p></td></tr><tr><td><p>14</p></td><td><p>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-class-features.Item.JuRJ625MuRQoseuT]{Spell Shield}</p></td></tr></tbody></table><table><caption><p>Expanded Spell List</p></caption><thead><tr><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Ranger Level</strong></p></th><th scope=\"col\"><p><strong>Extra Spell</strong></p></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><p>3</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.zWjDq2YlL1XWOcji]{Detect Magic}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.DtqyQCHrAX96VclO]{Identify}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>5</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.ImAJahFvkxJnFmaC]{Knock}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Wp9ckwdiUpIuPE5l]{See Invisibility}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>9</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.3URtFYL4DElhR4Jr]{Intercession}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.xT937OvSQSRfUoix]{Protection from Curses}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>13</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.VhcOj938RhpZDDhI]{Arcane Eye}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.ynE0kLi6F2AdqnR7]{Banishment}</em></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>17</p></td><td><p><em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.piOfkIqVwkpV4Znb]{Break Enchantment}</em>, <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.Mi4qWwfmDYv6GrkI]{Greater Restoration}</em></p></td></tr></tbody></table>",
